reviewText: Saw this with someone who became the first true love of my life way back in 1971. The movie is the sweetest; the soundtrack, excellent. Would love to find this on dvd. "Ain't it funny how young lovers start as friends...?"

Best story of my husband and I .
Whence these things happened to us. But we got back together again and have been married for over 45 years. Please  find this  interesting English.
